---
import adamImage from '/images/2022-04-adam-purple-wall-1-800-1067.jpg'
---

<style>
  img {
    box-shadow: var(--brand-box-shadow);
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 600px) {
    section {
      margin-right: auto;
      margin-left: auto;
      display: grid;
      align-items: center;
      grid-template-areas: 
        "title       img"
        "subtitle    img"
        "description img";
      grid-column-gap: 2em;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 250px;
    }
    h2 {
      grid-area: title;
      margin-bottom: 0;
      text-align: start;
    }
    img {
      position: relative;
      grid-area: img;
      min-width: 250px;
      max-width: 100%;
      z-index: 2;
    }
    .about__subtitle {
      padding-left: 2em;
      position: relative;
      grid-column: 1 / -1;
      grid-row: 2;
      left: -2em;
      width: calc(100% + 4em);
    }
  }
</style>


<section class="home-section">
  <h2 class="section__title">Who I am</h2>
  <p class="about__subtitle">Designer &amp; Developer</p>
  <div>
    <p>Lorem ipsum dolor, sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Eius nemo beatae eos fuga dicta ex odit odio aperiam praesentium placeat animi eveniet harum atque eligendi et fugit, inventore accusantium nam.</p>
  </div>
  <img src={adamImage} alt="Adam">
</section>